title: Beautiful  Property! Washer/Dryer Incl! Granite Countertops!
posting_body: Located on Frankford Road off of Dallas North Tollway,  offering unique interiors, including granite countertops, plank flooring, vaulted ceilings, crown molding, ceiling fans with lights, decorative fireplaces, and washer/dryer.

Spectacular amenities include a game room, two-stall carwash, business center, and two of each of the following: resort-style pool, indoor basketball & racquetball courts, lighted tennis and sand volleyball, fitness center, and indoor spa and sauna.
Covered parking and garages are available, as is WiFi in the clubhouse, business center, and poolside.
Please Call Desiree with DASH Realty
